Ragnar turns to face the newcomer. He keeps a cool attitude, but he 
knows that the lady seems to be somehow contemptful of the people 
here.

Ragnar: You do not think I can do it, quineg? Let me give you my 
resume. I am Star Colonel Ragnar of Clan Ghost Bear, Commander of the 
1st Rasalhague Bears, an veteran Cluster in the elite Alpha Galaxy. As 
I was taken as a bondsman by the Ghost Bears, I tested out again 
only three months after my capture with three kills in my initial 
trial of position. I have fought Clans Wolf, Jade Falcon, Smoke Jaguar 
and mauled all of them. I believe I am worthy. Two mere soldiers are 
no match for me, quiaff?
